---
Play a Spotify URI directly

Usage: spotuify play-uri [OPTIONS] <URI>

Arguments:
  <URI>  Spotify URI to play

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
